# ebpeak-trigger confirmation: compact (simple_cluster) / f_kappa=1 / PdV-inclusive trigger ACTIVE.
# Tests the ACTUAL code path (not just the passive shadow CSV): with transition_trigger including
# 'ebpeak', the energy phase ends the first segment edot_balance<=0 i.e. (Lloss+PdV)/Lgain>=1.
# PREDICTION (from cal_compact__k1 shadow): does NOT fire -- the PdV-inclusive ratio peaks ~0.91 just
# after dispersal (t~0.12) then DECLINES in the ISM, so it never reaches 1.0. The run should instead
# go to stop_t, confirming compact at f_kappa=1 transitions on NEITHER trigger ("1D cooling not enough").
# Opt-in dev run: no production behaviour change (default trigger stays cooling_balance).
model_name      cal_compact__ebpeak
path2output     outputs/kcal/cal_compact__ebpeak
mCloud    1e5
sfe    0.3
log_console    False
log_file    True
stop_t    0.5
cooling_boost_kappa    1.0
transition_trigger    cooling_balance,ebpeak
